    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** ** Morphisms in [(A \u2192 C)\u1d52\u1d56 \u00d7 (B \u2192 C)] from [(s\u2080, s\u2081)] to [(d\u2080, d\u2081)] induce functors [(s\u2080 / s\u2081) \u2192 (d\u2080 / d\u2081)] *)\n"
